      Built with <a href="https://astro.build" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Astro</a>
      · Deployed on <a href="https://vercel.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Vercel</a>
      · Sumit Vaise © {year} · Scarborough, Ontario
    </p>
  </div>
</footer>

<style>
  footer {
    background: var(--bg2); border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    padding: 28px 0; text-align: center;
  }
  p { font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-dim); }
  a { color: var(--text-muted); }
  a:hover { color: var(--accent3); }
</style>
